{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
# /acceptance-criteria — Criterios de Aceitacao

## Uso
```
/acceptance-criteria [feature]
```

## Fases

### Fase 0 — Reconhecimento
1. Entender a feature e seus requisitos
2. Identificar personas envolvidas
3. Ler historias de usuario relacionadas

### Fase 1 — Gerar Criterios

Salvar em: `{{paths.docsRoot}}/po/acceptance-criteria/{feature-kebab-case}.md`

```markdown
# Criterios de Aceitacao — {Feature}

## Cenarios

### @happy-path
**Cenario**: {descricao do caminho feliz}
**Dado** que {pre-condicao}
**Quando** {acao do usuario}
**Entao** {resultado esperado}
**E** {resultado adicional}

### @alternative
**Cenario**: {descricao de caminho alternativo}
**Dado** que {pre-condicao diferente}
**Quando** {acao do usuario}
**Entao** {resultado alternativo}

### @error-handling
**Cenario**: {descricao de erro}
**Dado** que {pre-condicao de erro}
**Quando** {acao que causa erro}
**Entao** {mensagem de erro exibida}
**E** {sistema permanece consistente}

### @edge-case
**Cenario**: {descricao de caso limite}
**Dado** que {condicao limite}
**Quando** {acao}
**Entao** {comportamento correto no limite}

## Checklist de Cobertura
- [ ] Campos obrigatorios validados
- [ ] Limites de caracteres
- [ ] Permissoes/autorizacao
- [ ] Estados de loading e erro
- [ ] Responsividade mobile
```
{{else}}
# /acceptance-criteria — Acceptance Criteria

## Usage
```
/acceptance-criteria [feature]
```

## Phases

### Phase 0 — Reconnaissance
1. Understand the feature and its requirements
2. Identify involved personas
3. Read related user stories

### Phase 1 — Generate Criteria

Save to: `{{paths.docsRoot}}/po/acceptance-criteria/{feature-kebab-case}.md`

```markdown
# Acceptance Criteria — {Feature}

## Scenarios

### @happy-path
**Scenario**: {happy path description}
**Given** {precondition}
**When** {user action}
**Then** {expected result}
**And** {additional result}

### @alternative
**Scenario**: {alternative path description}
**Given** {different precondition}
**When** {user action}
**Then** {alternative result}

### @error-handling
**Scenario**: {error description}
**Given** {error precondition}
**When** {action causing error}
**Then** {error message displayed}
**And** {system remains consistent}

### @edge-case
**Scenario**: {edge case description}
**Given** {boundary condition}
**When** {action}
**Then** {correct boundary behavior}

## Coverage Checklist
- [ ] Required fields validated
- [ ] Character limits
- [ ] Permissions/authorization
- [ ] Loading and error states
- [ ] Mobile responsiveness
```
